---
title: Beef Tenderloin & Creamy Mushroom Sauce with Roasted Potato Rounds & Arugula Parmesan Salad
description: Love a perfectly tender piece of beef? The kind where the knife just sinks right through? Us too! Enter: our juicy, succulent beef tenderloin seared to perfection and elevated with a creamy, umami-rich mushroom sauce. Serve it alongside crispy roasted potato rounds and a fresh, peppery arugula salad for the luxe steakhouse-style dinner of your dreams.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6579844dddd2bdfd232cb96c-aeba6edd.jpeg
